title: 2 BR/1bath Stevens Square, MCAD
posting_body: ['Stevens Sq Corner 2BR 1 block to MCAD, close to DWTN, UMN, MCTC', 'Property Address', '1912 3rd Ave So.', '| 21, 22, 31 | Minneapolis, MN 55404', 'Available:  8/1/22, 9/1/22', 'Offered By', 'GISP, Inc.', '|', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'One block from MCAD, only a five minute walk to downtown, or a short direct bus or bike ride to the UMN or MCTC this is sweet convenience.', 'We allow cats and dogs for additional rent and a one time $200.00 non refundable pet fee.', 'Off street parking is available for an additional fee.', 'We require a $45.00 application fee per adult when applying.', 'Income must be 2.0 x the rent.', ' No Evictions or UD’s in the last 5 years.', 'No major credit accounts written off, delinquent, or in collections in last 5 years.', 'No felony convictions in the last five years or Misdemeanors in the last year.', ' Those with felonies for murder, rape, arson, or assault will be denied.', 'No major lease violations from previous Landlord references.', 'We accept first time renters and co-signers.', 'This is a smoke free building.', 'To apply on line go to <URL>', 'Units vary', 'Amenities', 'hardwood floors', 'natural woodwork', 'breakfast bar', 'on-line rent payment', 'on line maintenance requests', 'on site laundry', 'free storage', 'On direct bus line to West Bank', 'One block to MCAD', '24 hour emergency service', '5 minute walk to downtown', 'restaurants & coffee shops within a block', 'Gas Stove', 'secured entry', 'many shops and restaurants nearby', 'Common area surveilance', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 622', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent starts at $999', 'Available: July & Aug, Sept', 'Application Fee: $45.00', 'Security Deposit: $999', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
